        "Description": "Good evening 47\rSome of the staff at the manor have been stealing, and the group is lead by the butler himself. The lady of the manor is paying a lot of money to get rid of them as soon as possible. She has requested for their deaths to  seem like random coincidence so try to make them seem like accidents. Do note that there is a private investigator on the manor investigating a murder, careful he doesn&apos;t spot you, however maybe you can take advange of the murder, to cover up the deaths.",
